reviewText: its worth getting it iam glad i bought this dvd i will be ordering in future again. iam a satisfy customer

I bought this dvd because I am a huge dog the bounty hunter fan. Let me warn you that this disc has only 2 episodes on it. The thief who stole christmas and The hunt for santa. If you have these two episodes already I would not buy this dvd but if you don't then you need to buy this dvd.
